text: Hornussen was a municipality of the district of Laufenburg in the canton of Aargau in Switzerland. On 1 January 2022, the former municipalities of Bözen, Effingen, Elfingen and Hornussen merged to form the new municipality of Böztal. ==References== == Other websites == * *Official website of the municipality of Hornussen Category:Former municipalities of Aargau
